{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we went from-- also went for a while-- it was-- then, it was like a camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got, somewhere, a photo even from that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we sort of were led.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we really-- at night-- we walked only at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember, we went through some enormous hills to Milano.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we-- sort of, at night, you didn't know, because you went through some hills.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You really didn't know what your next step, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could have-- you could have gone really any way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't see in front of you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you just prayed, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you hoped that you're not going to just-- Somehow, all of us survived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somehow, to this group, sort of nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How many people were traveling with you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a lot of people, about 50 people, 80 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was always-- we were always around-- surrounded by people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a group traveling to Austria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from Austria, we went to-- to Milano.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there we stayed for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Milano, it was in a old synagogue that we stayed, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, we stayed-- it was-- it's not to compare, really, but we were, again, maybe 100 people in a room, in this room that we stayed together.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, by the time they were all-- most of them were couples, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a bit awkward.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, we didn't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- Were you-- were you crossing borders legally or illegally?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- illegally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was illegally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- nothing was legal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean the quota, whatever was legal was filled out-- filled up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If we wanted to wait a couple of years?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
